Squizzy::
She heard the door lock.  She suddenly realized she was trapped 
inside the chamber.  She started banging on the door. "HEY! LET ME 
OUT OF HERE! I DIDN"T DO ANYTHING! LET ME OUT!"  She kept banging on 
the doors.  She started to feel drowsy and light headed.  She banged 
on the doors, but not as hard.  She  finally stopped banging as she 
passed out inside the chamber. 


--- In nbwrpg@egroups.com, Yanshosh@a... wrote:
> ::Dark One::
> 
> The CR chamber's door closes behind Squizzy, Dark One walking over 
to a panel 
> and pressing a few buttons. The CR chamber was one designed for 
hostages and 
> prisoners, and put the occupant into stasis. He activates the cyber-
liquid, 
> designed to knock out the occupant. Tapping a few more keys, he 
locks the CR 
> door.
> 
> "If she tries to escape, shoot her untill she's out," he orders the 
autoguns, 
> running out of the room and heading for the exit of the Alliance 
base.
